id§NOT_1499076262_6820831°datum§07.07.2017°DatumE§2017-07-07-00-00-00_NOT_1499076262_6820831°quelle§persistent°name§PHP: PEAR°kategorien§.php°info§°text§<br/>-----<br/><p>&nbsp;</p><p>check PEAR installs packages into correct directories:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>pear config-show</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Changing a value is as easy as retrieving it:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>$ pear config-set preferred_state beta</p><p>config-set succeeded</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>pear config-set &nbsp; &nbsp;bin_dir &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;C:\programme\xampp\php</p><p>pear config-set &nbsp; doc_dir &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;C:\programme\xampp\php\docs</p><p>pear config-set &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; php_dir &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;C:\programme\xampp\php\pear</p><p>pear config-set cache_dir &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;C:\programme\xampp\php\pear\cache</p><p>pear config-set &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;cfg_dir &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;C:\programme\xampp\php\cfg</p><p>pear config-set &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;data_dir &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; C:\programme\xampp\php\data</p><p>pear config-set &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;download_dir &nbsp; &nbsp; C:\programme\xampp\php\tmp</p><p>pear config-set &nbsp;temp_dir &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; C:\programme\xampp\php\tmp</p><p>pear config-set &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; test_dir &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; C:\programme\xampp\php\tests</p><p>pear config-set &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;www_dir &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;C:\programme\xampp\htdocs</p><p>pear config-set &nbsp; &nbsp;php_ini &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;C:\programme\xampp\php\php.ini</p><p>pear config-set &nbsp; &nbsp;php_bin &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;C:\programme\xampp\php\php.exe</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>When changing a config setting, it does not immediately get applied to already installed packages. This is especially true when changing variables like data_dir. Use&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>pear upgrade --force&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>to reinstall all packages in such cases.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>von http://pear.php.net/manual/en/guide.users.commandline.config.php</p>°date§11.9.2015°files§°art§Anleitung